<i>50,000 yen to tutor a shut-in high school girl once a week.</i>

20
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:26,240
<i>That's 200,000 a month.</i>

21
00:01:26,240 --> 00:01:30,549
<i>Do tell us more.</i>

22
